Why This Works

Quick overview for staff.
✍️

Tab-Through Entry

Fast keyboard navigation through every field. No hunting for a transfer pad or handwriting under pressure.

🕑

Auto Date & Timestamp

Printed date and time generated automatically for consistent, accurate documentation.

📄

Dynamic Rx Layout

Select 1–5 prescriptions and the form adjusts. Multiple transfers captured on a single page.

👁️

Always Legible

Typed documentation eliminates interpretation guesswork during follow-up calls and data entry.

✅

Mirrors System Layout

Structure aligns with system-generated transfer request printouts for consistency across methods.

🛠️

Optional — Not Required

Doesn’t replace existing processes. Just a cleaner alternative for teams who prefer typed intake.
